AccumuloCellTransformers - Class in cellmate.accumulo.reader.celltransformer
Static helper methods that offer concrete Cell transformers that cover a variety of common use cases for reading Accumulo Key/Value pairs into Cell groups.

The type-specific ValueQualToLabel methods set the cell label to the db qualifer, and the cell value to the db item value.
